Value List model (\w+)
Value List serial_number (\w+)
Value version (.+?)
Value Filldown hostname (\S+)


Start
  ^\s+(NXOS: version|system:\s+version)\s+${version}\s*$$
  ^\s+cisco\s+${model}\s+[cC]hassis
  ^\s+cisco\s+Nexus\d+\s+${model}
  ^\s+cisco\s+Nexus\s+${model}\s+[cC]hassis
  ^\s+cisco\s+.+-${model}\s*
  ^\s*Processor\s[Bb]oard\sID\s+${serial_number}$$